olds join rosie huntingtonwhiteley for ms the daily telegraph london  august  archived from the original on  march  retrieved  july    peacock louisa  july  ms drops ad featuring twiggy minogue and vv brown the daily telegraph london   emma thompson annie lennox and rita ora unveiled as marks  spencer leading ladies campaign live retrieved  march    boycott israel website boycottisraelcouk  september  archived from the original on  september  retrieved  april    brighton activists deface marks and spencer store  working with government archived  june  at the wayback machine marks  spencer   october  comments  october  osborne’s cuts will strengthen britain’s economy by allowing the private sector to generate more jobs the daily telegraph uk retrieved  april    ms cuts  jobs as fashion sales dive helen power and marcus leroux the times  january  archived  june  at the wayback machine  why i’m boycotting the  businesses who support the cuts kate belgrave liberalconspiracyorg  october  retrieved  april    contactless charging errors at marks and spencer bbc news  may  retrieved  march    withnall adam delmarmorgan alex  december  ms says muslim staff may refuse to serve customers pork and alcohol the independent london retrieved  december    mendick robert  december  muslim staff at marks  spencer can refuse to sell alcohol and pork the daily telegraph london retrieved  december    ms faces furious backlash from customers over muslim policy yahoo news  december    ms apology over muslim alcohol refusal bbc news  december  retrieved  december   bibliographyedit burns paul  corporate entrepreneurship building an entrepreneurial organization basingstoke palgrave macmillan isbn   external linksedit wikimedia commons has media related to marks  spencer official website store locator plan a ecoinitiative spark something good charity initiative v t e supermarkets in the united kingdom big four asda morrisons sainsburys tesco convenience bargain booze bestone budgens the coope