yim passionate about designing products through making physical prototypes physics based theoretical models d models in solidworks and proecreo and active communication with the needs of my clientele i strive to create the best design im an experienced full cycle product development mechanical product design engineer ive lead the mechanical design of several projects as well as played supporting rolesmy portfolio and personal work focuses on the following sustainable design  saving the environment and minimizing further cost to the user down the line  solutions for urban living  improving and complementing the life of an individual living in a large city  energy harvest  harnessing wasted moments and motion and converting them into usable sources of energy consumer facing products which require high level aesthetic and surfacing qualityskills▪ applications solidworks proecreo windchill rhinod matlab autocad siemens nx adobe suite microsoft office latex catalyst objet studio ansys mechanical and magnetic cosmos▪ workshop woodwork metalwork breadboarding d digitizing rapid prototyping objet polyjet stratasys zcorp fdm sla sls▪ special skills dfm dfa fa doe miniature tools imaging microscope tolerancing gdt materials selection fea photo  data capture and sensor setup and analysis▪ os windows mac and linux▪ over  cad hours loggedspecialties optimization efficiency mechanical design interdisciplinary engineering integration design presentation invention cross functional team leadership a large amount of experience in solidworks d modeling  design physical prototyping and manufacturing applications my work has focused on consumer product design considerations with respect to human user interaction such as ergonomics ease of use and product elegance i have been told that i am a catalyst i seek out new technologies and find the best way to integrate themexperienceproduct design engineergooglefebruary  – present  years  monthsdesign prototype d modeling validation testing ma